
Quick install instructions:

perl Makefile.PL
make
make install 

Quick usage instructions:

perl -MExtUtils::Git=:all Makefile.PL

Where Makefile.PL is the Makefile.PL generated by h2xs for your Perl module.

make git_import

To import all files listed in the MANIFEST file of your module into Git.

make git_ci

To check-in all changed files into the local Git repository and push them
upstream to the master repository.

make git_status

To see the status of files in relation to the Git repository.
